item.title: Big Launch!
item.description: After a few weeks of development, tweaking, and learning I am finally proud to announce my website and the first functional version of docusaurus-portfolio. I started this project as a way to learn about Docusaurus's code base while also spending time crafting my own personal site.

item.title: Hello World!
item.description: Blogs, are also available while using docusaurus-portfolio! Combine an about me page with a blog to make a cool personal website.
